AND KISS YOU.
WHY NOT?

35:55.100 --> 35:56.767
MEREDITH.
WHAT?

35:56.800 --> 35:58.667
CHOOSE DOOR NUMBER ONE.

35:58.700 --> 36:00.600
A WISE MAN ONCE SAID

36:00.633 --> 36:02.533
YOU CAN HAVE ANYTHING IN LIFE

36:02.567 --> 36:04.467
