LIKE YOU AND IZZIE,

36:22.633 --> 36:24.633
THOSE PEOPLE
LOVE EACH OTHER.

36:24.667 --> 36:26.333
SHE MISSES HER FRIEND.

36:26.367 --> 36:28.733
WHAT HE MEANT IS,

36:28.767 --> 36:30.600
NOTHING COMES
WITHOUT A PRICE.

36:30.633 --> 36:32.533
(Alex clicks his tongue)

36:32.567 --> 36:35.367
THE ROAD TO HELL
IS PAVED WITH GOOD INTENTIONS.
(pager beeps)

36:35.400 --> 36:37.300
SO BEFORE YOU GO INTO BATTLE,

36:37.333 --> 36:39.800
YOU BETTER DECIDE HOW MUCH
YOU'RE WILLING TO LOSE.

36:39.833 --> 36:42.333
DR. KAREV...

36:42.367 --> 36:46.067
YOU DID
SUCH A GOOD JOB TODAY THAT...

36:46.067 --> 36:47.800
