UNTIL I SAY OTHERWISE.

36:54.500 --> 36:56.433
CONGRATULATIONS.

36:56.467 --> 36:59.300
***

36:59.333 --> 37:01.167
YOU GOT IT.

37:01.200 --> 37:03.800
