37:03.833 --> 37:05.167
AND YOU'RE OKAY?

37:05.200 --> 37:07.667
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?
I'M GREAT.

37:07.700 --> 37:08.833
I MEAN, LOOK AT THIS--

37:08.867 --> 37:12.100
SOME NICE-SIZED BATTERIES,
COLORFUL WIRES.

37:12.133 --> 37:14.067
IT'S WHAT YOUR
BEST-DRESSED LVAD PATIENTS

37:14.100 --> 37:16.300
