YOU KNOW?

37:16.333 --> 37:17.267
REALLY?

37:17.300 --> 37:20.367
'CAUSE IT SEEMS
SO LAST FALL.

37:20.400 --> 37:23.567
***

37:23.600 --> 37:27.433
