OF WHAT YOU KNOW IS RIGHT.

37:43.767 --> 37:46.733
***

37:51.367 --> 37:56.067
YOU DID EVERYTHING
YOU COULD.

37:56.100 --> 37:58.800
***

37:58.833 --> 38:02.600
