THE MOST TALENTED STUDENT

38:10.367 --> 38:11.533
AT MUSIC SCHOOL.

38:11.567 --> 38:14.800
BUT HE SAID WHAT HE LACKED
IN NATURAL ABILITY,

38:14.833 --> 38:19.067
HE MADE UP FOR IN DISCIPLINE.

38:19.100 --> 38:21.667
HE PRACTICED...

38:21.700 --> 38:25.067
ALL THE TIME.

38:25.100 --> 38:28.067
ALL THE TIME,
HE PRACTICED.

38:28.067 --> 38:30.600
I WASN'T LIKE YOU.

38:30.633 --> 38:33.500
I WASN'T THE MOST TALENTED
STUDENT IN SCHOOL.

38:33.533 --> 38:36.300
I WASN'T THE BRIGHTEST.

38:36.333 --> 38:40.100
BUT I WAS THE BEST.

38:40.133 --> 38:43.133
***

38:48.800 --> 38:51.467
YOU PRACTICED.

38:51.500 --> 38:54.600
I PRACTICED.

38:54.633 --> 38:58.333
AND LETTING SOMEONE IN
MEANS ABANDONING THE WALLS

38:58.367 --> 39:00.267
YOU'VE SPENT
A LIFETIME BUILDING.

39:00.300 --> 39:02.800
I GOT HOME, HE WAS LISTLESS
AND HADN'T EATEN ALL DAY.

39:02.833 --> 39:04.733
OH, NO. LET'S HAVE A LOOK.

39:04.767 --> 39:09.067
***

39:09.067 --> 39:10.800
OF COURSE,
THE TOUGHEST SACRIFICES

39:10.833 --> 39:12.633
