39:20.300 --> 39:21.567
YEAH.

39:21.600 --> 39:25.167
***

39:27.433 --> 39:29.100
GEORGE.

39:29.133 --> 39:30.067
HEY.

39:30.100 --> 39:31.067
HEY.

39:31.067 --> 39:32.100
OH.

39:32.133 --> 39:33.733
