39:33.767 --> 39:35.400
HEY.

39:35.433 --> 39:37.700
SO WE SPENT THE NIGHT
AT CALLIE'S LAST NIGHT.

39:37.733 --> 39:40.500
SO I FIGURED WE'D JUST
SPEND THE NIGHT HERE.

39:40.533 --> 39:42.500
OKAY, SO, UH...

39:42.533 --> 39:44.433
YOU'RE BACK, THEN,
JUST FOR TONIGHT?

39:44.467 --> 39:46.300
WELL, CALLIE'S HERE
FOR TONIGHT.

39:46.333 --> 39:47.833
I'M, UH...

39:47.867 --> 39:49.833
I DON'T KNOW.

39:49.867 --> 39:52.733
IT'S MY ROOM.
I PAY RENT.

39:52.767 --> 39:55.267
WELCOME HOME.

39:55.300 --> 39:58.767
WHEN WE DON'T HAVE TIME
TO COME UP WITH A STRATEGY,

39:58.800 --> 40:00.100
TO PICK A SIDE

40:00.133 --> 40:03.667
OR TO MEASURE
THE POTENTIAL LOSS.

40:03.700 --> 40:07.533
***

40:07.567 --> 40:10.367
YOU WOULD NOT BELIEVE
THE DAY I HAD.

40:10.400 --> 40:12.200
I WENT OUT OF MY WAY
TO GIVE A PATIENT

40:12.233 --> 40:13.367
EXACTLY WHAT SHE WANTS,

40:13.400 --> 40:15.733
ONLY TO HAVE IT
EXPLODE IN MY FACE.

40:15.767 --> 40:18.133
I MEAN, LAWSUIT, THREATS,
RICHARD'S PISSED.

40:18.167 --> 40:20.600
DON'T EVEN GET ME STARTED
ABOUT ALEX KAREV.
GET IN THE SHOWER.

40:20.633 --> 40:21.567
WHAT?

40:21.600 --> 40:23.600
GET IN THE SHOWER
WITH ME.

40:23.633 --> 40:27.033
HONEY,
IT'S A VERY SMALL SHOWER.

40:27.067 --> 40:30.400
YOU WANT TO HAVE HOT SEX?

40:30.433 --> 40:33.133
THANK YOU. OH.

40:33.167 --> 40:35.300
WHEN THAT HAPPENS,
WHEN THE BATTLE CHOOSES US

40:35.333 --> 40:37.233
AND NOT THE OTHER WAY AROUND,

40:37.267 --> 40:38.833
THAT'S WHEN THE SACRIFICE

40:38.867 --> 40:43.233
